Minimum absolute Pearson |r| required for a correlation to be considered statistically
meaningful and included in the results (when  is
). Range: [0, 1]. Default: 0.30.

Populate  from Garmin FIT-style zone fields.
Garmin exports provide time-in-zone in seconds for zones indexed 0–4;
this method converts them to whole minutes and stores them correctly.
